Naming Scheme: [number]_CK2Plus_[category]_[descriptor].txt

Numbers to maintain ability to quickly find relevant files:

00: Info files
01: Broad effect
02: Narrow effect
03: Flavor or info-only events

categories:

core: events that apply over the entire mod regardless of feature or mechanic
feature: large functions that use more than just events (e.g. new religions, governments, laws etc.)
mechanic: functions that are executed primarily within events
flavor: No large-ranging impact outside of player immersion/interactivity or very small game balancing

namespaces: plusDescriptor
